OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Retail chain Wilko has apologised for  
OL,6, "some miscommunication" in which it    
OL,7, told staff they could continue to work 
OL,8, if they tested positive for Covid.     
OL,10,FIn a memo, reported by The Mirror, the 
OL,11,Fcompany said staff with the virus could
OL,12,Fcontinue to work in stores if they felt
OL,13,Fwell enough to.                        
OL,15,FWilko confirmed the memo was sent out  
OL,16,Fand the firm has since made a U-turn.  
OL,18,F"When we get something wrong, we hold  
OL,19,Four hands up, admit it, and work to    
OL,20,Fcorrect the situation," the firm said. 
